name: Planet Obsidian
description: Planet Obsidian is the planet of protection and creativity. This planet is powerful and grounds the soul. Here you are forced to face your true self and journey into the subconscious mind. This planet brings imbalances and shadow qualities to the surface for release and renewal. It is here that you will be protected as negativity is repelled and negative thoughts are dispersed. This planet includes LED changing colored lights, and it glows differently under UV light, regular light, and no light.
